name: Daria Adolsfson
description:
Speaking about my character I am sweet, kind and honest girl. I am sweet like sugar, warm like sunshine, fresh like sea breeze, tender like velvet and passionate like a woman who knows what love is! I am very romantic and fragile but realistic and strong at the same time. I know that it is hard to set such qualities together but I could easily join them in my personality harmonically.
Maybe you are somewhere far away waiting for me? So now I am here to find you!!!!!!!!!!!
